msgstr "Activo"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1398
msgid "Disabled"
msgstr "Desactivado"

#. translators: %d is the number of days for log retention.
#: es-football-bypass.php:1400
#, php-format
msgid "Retention: %d days."
msgstr "Retención: %d días."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1402
msgid "Logging is disabled. Enable it in the Settings tab."
msgstr "El registro está desactivado. Actívalo en la pestaña de Configuración."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1406
msgid "No events recorded yet."
msgstr "Todavía no hay eventos registrados."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1408
msgid "The log file exists but contains no recent events."
msgstr "El archivo de log existe pero no contiene eventos recientes."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1413
msgid "Date"
msgstr "Fecha"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1413
msgid "Type"
msgstr "Tipo"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1413
msgid "Message"
msgstr "Mensaje"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1413
msgid "Context"
msgstr "Contexto"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1427
msgid "Showing the 250 most recent events."
msgstr "Se muestran los 250 eventos más recientes."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1442
msgid ""
"Global API Key requires email. User tokens are in My Profile. Account tokens "
"are in Manage Account > Account API Tokens (requires Super Administrator). "
"Minimum permissions: Zone:Read, DNS:Read, DNS:Edit."
msgstr ""
"Global API Key requiere email. Los tokens de usuario están en Mi Perfil. Los "
"tokens de cuenta están en Gestionar cuenta > Account API Tokens (requiere "
"Super Administrator). Permisos mínimos: Zone:Read, DNS:Read, DNS:Edit."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1459
msgid "Never shown in traces or console."
msgstr "Nunca se muestra en trazas ni consola."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1474
msgid ""
"Required only for account tokens. You can find it in the URL of the "
"Cloudflare dashboard: dash.cloudflare.com/ACCOUNT_ID"
msgstr ""
"Obligatorio solo para tokens de cuenta. Lo encuentras en la URL del "
"dashboard de Cloudflare: dash.cloudflare.com/ACCOUNT_ID"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1481
msgid "Could not be detected"
msgstr "No se pudo detectar"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1482
msgid ""
"The server outgoing IP could not be determined. Verify that the server has "
"Internet access."
msgstr ""
"No se ha podido determinar la IP de salida del servidor. Comprueba que el "
"servidor tiene acceso a Internet."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1485
msgid ""
"This is the IP your server uses to communicate with the Cloudflare API. You "
"can restrict your API Token to this IP for added security."
msgstr ""
"Esta es la IP que tu servidor usa para comunicarse con la API de Cloudflare. "
"Puedes restringir tu API Token a esta IP para mayor seguridad."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1493
msgid ""
"Multiple outgoing IPs have been detected. Your server may use any of them to "
"communicate with the Cloudflare API. Add all of them when restricting your "
"API Token."
msgstr ""
"Se han detectado varias IPs de salida. Tu servidor puede usar cualquiera de "
"ellas para comunicarse con la API de Cloudflare. Añade todas al restringir "
"tu API Token."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1507
msgid ""
"Select the records to manage in the <strong>Operation</strong> tab (using "
"the cache)."
msgstr ""
"Marca los registros a gestionar en la pestaña <strong>Operación</strong> "
"(usando el caché)."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1518
msgid ""
"Minutes that must pass after disabling Cloudflare before checking if it can "
"be reactivated (5-1440)."
msgstr ""
"Minutos que deben pasar tras desactivar Cloudflare antes de volver a "
"comprobar si puede reactivarse (5-1440)."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1530
msgid ""
"Ignore \"blocked\" states whose most recent stateChange in hayahora.futbol "
"is older than this (1-72 hours, default 6). Prevents orphan records from "
"keeping the bypass active indefinitely when a close event was never "
"published."
msgstr ""
"Ignora los estados «bloqueado» cuyo stateChange más reciente en "
"hayahora.futbol sea anterior a este plazo (1-72 horas, por defecto 6). Evita "
"que registros huérfanos mantengan el bypass activo indefinidamente cuando "
"nunca se publicó el evento de cierre."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1538
msgid "Simple (recommended for clients)"
msgstr "Simple (recomendado para clientes)"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1539
msgid "Advanced (show diagnostics, logs and technical details)"
msgstr "Avanzado (mostrar diagnóstico, logs y detalles técnicos)"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1540
msgid ""
"Simple mode hides the feed diagnostics panel, the logs tab and the technical "
"console — leaving only the block status and the manual proxy ON/OFF buttons. "
"Logs are still written to disk: switch to Advanced temporarily if you need "
"to diagnose a problem."
msgstr ""
"El modo simple oculta el panel de diagnóstico del feed, la pestaña de logs y "
"la consola técnica, dejando solo el estado de bloqueo y los botones manuales "
"de proxy ON/OFF. Los logs se siguen escribiendo en disco: cambia a Avanzado "
"temporalmente si necesitas diagnosticar un problema."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1549
msgid ""
"Send an email to the site admin when the bypass turns on or off automatically"
msgstr ""
"Enviar un email al administrador del sitio cuando el bypass se active o "
"desactive automáticamente"

#. translators: %s is the admin email address.
#: es-football-bypass.php:1551
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Emails are sent to %s only on actual state changes from the cron (not on "
"manual override). A 2-minute throttle prevents bursts if the feed oscillates."
msgstr ""
"Los emails se envían a %s solo cuando hay un cambio real de estado por el "
"cron (no en forzado manual). Un throttle de 2 minutos evita ráfagas si el "
"feed oscila."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1563
msgid ""
"Minimum number of distinct ISPs (providers) with currently blocked IPs "
"needed to consider there is a real mass block (1-20, default 2). Lower "
"values are more sensitive; 1 triggers on any single-ISP glitch. Only applies "
"when the feed publishes ISP information; ignored otherwise."
msgstr ""
"Número mínimo de proveedores (ISPs) distintos con IPs actualmente bloqueadas "
"necesarios para considerar que hay un bloqueo masivo real (1-20, por defecto "
"2). Valores bajos son más sensibles; 1 dispara ante el fallo de un único "
"ISP. Solo se aplica cuando el feed publica información por ISP; en caso "
"contrario se ignora."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1570
msgid ""
"Disable Proxy during football (General=YES), without waiting for this domain "
"detection"
msgstr ""
"Desactivar Proxy cuando hay fútbol (General=SI), sin esperar detección de "
"este dominio"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1571
msgid ""
"IMPORTANT: With this option enabled, the proxy will be automatically "
"disabled when hayahora.futbol indicates active blocks (General=YES), even if "
"your specific domain has not been detected as blocked."
msgstr ""
"IMPORTANTE: Con esta opción activada, el proxy se desactivará "
"automáticamente cuando hayahora.futbol indique que hay bloqueos activos "
"(General=SI), aunque tu dominio específico no haya sido detectado como "
"bloqueado."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1572
msgid ""
"Useful to avoid false negatives when you know your site is blocked during "
"football events but IP detection doesn't always work correctly."
msgstr ""
"Útil para evitar falsos negativos cuando sabes que tu sitio es bloqueado "
"durante eventos de fútbol pero la detección de IP no siempre funciona "
"correctamente."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1579
msgid "Save actions to log (cron and manual)"
msgstr "Guardar acciones en el registro (cron y manuales)"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1580
msgid ""
"Logs are stored in the uploads directory, protected with .htaccess, and "
"displayed in the Logs tab."
msgstr ""
"Los registros se guardan en el directorio uploads protegidos con .htaccess y "
"se muestran en la pestaña Logs."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1591
msgid "Number of days to keep logs (minimum 1)."
msgstr "Número de días a conservar registros (mínimo 1)."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1606
msgid ""
"Optional. Use a real server cron when WP-Cron is unreliable (low-traffic "
"sites, hosts that disable it). Leave empty to disable the external endpoint."
msgstr ""
"Opcional. Usa un cron real del servidor cuando WP-Cron no sea fiable (sitios "
"con poco tráfico, hostings que lo desactivan). Déjalo vacío para desactivar "
"el endpoint externo."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1609
msgid "URL to request:"
msgstr "URL a consultar:"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1613
msgid "Crontab example (server cron):"
msgstr "Ejemplo de crontab (cron del servidor):"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1617
msgid "To regenerate the token, empty the field and save."
msgstr "Para regenerar el token, vacía el campo y guarda."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1624
msgid ""
"Delete all plugin data when this plugin is uninstalled from Plugins → "
"Installed Plugins → Delete"
msgstr ""
"Borrar todos los datos del plugin cuando se desinstale desde Plugins → "
"Plugins instalados → Borrar"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1625
msgid ""
"Only applies at uninstall time, not when the plugin is deactivated. When "
"checked (default), uninstalling removes settings, Cloudflare credentials, "
"DNS cache and logs. Uncheck this if you plan to reinstall later and want to "
"keep the configuration. The scheduled cron and temporary caches are always "
"cleaned up regardless of this setting."
msgstr ""
"Solo se aplica al desinstalar, no al desactivar. Si está marcado (por "
"defecto), al desinstalar se borran la configuración, las credenciales de "
"Cloudflare, la caché DNS y los logs. Desmárcalo si piensas reinstalar "
"después y quieres conservar la configuración. El cron programado y las "
"cachés temporales se limpian siempre, independientemente de este ajuste."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1643
msgid "Local environment detected"
msgstr "Entorno local detectado"

#. translators: %s is the detected domain
#: es-football-bypass.php:1646
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The current domain is %s, which corresponds to a local environment or an IP "
"address. This plugin needs a public domain accessible from the Internet to "
"work correctly (DNS resolution, Cloudflare API and block checking)."
msgstr ""
"El dominio actual es %s, que corresponde a un entorno local o una dirección "
"IP. Este plugin necesita un dominio público accesible desde Internet para "
"funcionar correctamente (resolución DNS, API de Cloudflare y comprobación de "
"bloqueos)."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1649
msgid ""
"Install the plugin on your production or staging site with a real domain to "
"use it."
msgstr ""
"Instala el plugin en tu sitio de producción o staging con un dominio real "
"para utilizarlo."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1651
msgid "Go to Settings"
msgstr "Ir a Configuración"

#. translators: %s is the site name.
#: es-football-bypass.php:3117
#, php-format
msgid "[%s] Cloudflare proxy disabled due to football blocks"
msgstr "[%s] Proxy de Cloudflare desactivado por bloqueos del fútbol"

#: es-football-bypass.php:3118
msgid ""
"Hello,\n"
"\n"
"Active IP blocks from La Liga have been detected and the Cloudflare proxy "
"has been automatically disabled on the configured DNS records."
msgstr ""
"Hola,\n"
"\n"
"Se han detectado bloqueos de IPs activos por parte de La Liga y el proxy de "
"Cloudflare se ha desactivado automáticamente en los registros DNS "
"configurados."

#. translators: %s is the site name.
#: es-football-bypass.php:3119 es-football-bypass.php:3133
#, php-format
msgid "Site: %s"
msgstr "Sitio: %s"

#. translators: %s is the site URL.
#: es-football-bypass.php:3120 es-football-bypass.php:3134
#, php-format
msgid "URL: %s"
msgstr "URL: %s"

#. translators: %s is the site URL.
#: es-football-bypass.php:3121
msgid "State: Proxy OFF (DNS Only)"
msgstr "Estado: Proxy OFF (DNS Only)"

#. translators: %s is the internal reason code.
#: es-football-bypass.php:3123
#, php-format
msgid "Reason: %s"
msgstr "Motivo: %s"

#: es-football-bypass.php:3125
msgid ""
"The selected DNS records have switched from Proxied (CDN) to DNS Only so "
"your site remains reachable during the blocks."
msgstr ""
"Los registros DNS seleccionados han pasado de Proxied (CDN) a DNS Only para "
"que tu sitio siga siendo accesible durante los bloqueos."

#: es-football-bypass.php:3126
msgid ""
"The proxy will be re-enabled automatically once the blocks end and the "
"configured cooldown passes."
msgstr ""
"El proxy se volverá a activar automáticamente cuando terminen los bloqueos y "
"pase el periodo de enfriamiento configurado."

#. translators: %s is the plugin Operation page URL.
#: es-football-bypass.php:3127 es-football-bypass.php:3137
#, php-format
msgid "Current status: %s"
msgstr "Estado actual: %s"

#. translators: %s is the plugin version.
#: es-football-bypass.php:3128 es-football-bypass.php:3138
#, php-format
msgid "ES Football Bypass for Cloudflare v%s"
msgstr "ES Football Bypass for Cloudflare v%s"

#. translators: %s is the site name.
#: es-football-bypass.php:3131
#, php-format
msgid "[%s] Cloudflare proxy re-enabled"
msgstr "[%s] Proxy de Cloudflare reactivado"

#: es-football-bypass.php:3132
msgid ""
"Hello,\n"
"\n"
"No active La Liga IP blocks are detected. The Cloudflare proxy has been re-"
"enabled automatically."
msgstr ""
"Hola,\n"
"\n"
"No se detectan bloqueos de IP activos de La Liga. El proxy de Cloudflare se "
"ha vuelto a activar automáticamente."

#. translators: %s is the site URL.
#: es-football-bypass.php:3135
msgid "State: Proxy ON (CDN)"
msgstr "Estado: Proxy ON (CDN)"

#: es-football-bypass.php:3136
msgid ""
"The selected DNS records are back on Proxied (CDN). Normal operation resumed."
msgstr ""
"Los registros DNS seleccionados han vuelto a Proxied (CDN). Funcionamiento "
"normal restablecido."

